		<h2>Game Info:</h2><div class="t"><div class="b"><div class="l"><div class="r"><div class="bl"><div class="br"><div class="tl"><div class="tr">Allows your cities to build <span class="color_positive_text">Aqueducts</span>, increasing the <img src="/civilopedia/images/food.png" alt="food" /> Food that is carried over as your city grows. Also allows Workers to construct <span class="color_positive_text">Forts</span> on map tiles, increasing the defense of units stationed there. Additionally, bridges are automatically added to roads which cross rivers, allowing units to pass over them without slowing down.</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
